('ingles', 'bachillerato', '{1}', 'William Shakespeare was born in Stratford upon Avon in the sixteenth century and became the greatest English playwright'),
('ingles', 'bachillerato', '{1}', 'The Globe Theatre in London was the original stage where many of Shakespeare plays were first performed'),
('ingles', 'bachillerato', '{1}', 'Charles Dickens wrote Oliver Twist to expose the terrible conditions faced by poor children in Victorian England'),
