('ingles', 'bachillerato', '{1}', 'Isaac Newton discovered the laws of gravity while watching an apple fall from a tree in his garden'),
('ingles', 'bachillerato', '{1}', 'The British Empire at its peak controlled about one quarter of the total land surface of the Earth'),
('ingles', 'bachillerato', '{1}', 'Queen Victoria reigned for over sixty years and her era is known as the Victorian period in history'),
('ingles', 'bachillerato', '{1}', 'Jane Austen wrote Pride and Prejudice which explores love marriage and social class in Regency England'),
